title: Paul Simon & Art Garfunkel - Old Friends (Dutch Treat ^B074
description:
After a while even I has (!) to admit, he will never receive better material than he does not already has from Simon & Garfunkel (also solo). Felt a bit like the Bob Dylan recordings. So although very dusty (sound included) I could not longer reject their rightful claim of having their own portrait, among the ones I already love (to play). I counted the tracks and surrendered.... Enjoy,
